#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn13.9"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn13.9:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 13 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 13 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.9:0.2"
msgid "1. Abhisamayavagga "
msgstr "1. Comprehension "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 9. Pabbatasutta → pabbatūpamasuttaṃ (bj) | pabbatūpama 1 (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn13.9:0.3"
msgid "9. Pabbatasutta "
msgstr "9. A Mountain "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn13.9:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.9:1.2"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, puriso himavato pabbatarājassa satta sāsapamattiyo pāsāṇasakkharā upanikkhipeyya. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, suppose a person was to place seven pebbles the size of mustard seeds on the Himalayas, the king of mountains. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.9:1.3"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn13.9:1.4"
msgid "katamaṃ nu kho bahutaraṃ, yā vā satta sāsapamattiyo pāsāṇasakkharā upanikkhittā yo vā himavā pabbatarājā”ti? "
msgstr "Which is more: the seven pebbles the size of mustard seeds, or the Himalayas, the king of mountains?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.138, sc2
msgctxt "sn13.9:2.1"
msgid "“Etadeva, bhante, bahutaraṃ yadidaṃ himavā pabbatarājā; "
msgstr "“Sir, the Himalayas, the king of mountains, is certainly more. "

msgctxt "sn13.9:2.2"
msgid "appamattikā satta sāsapamattiyo pāsāṇasakkharā upanikkhittā. "
msgstr "The seven pebbles the size of mustard seeds are tiny. "

msgctxt "sn13.9:2.3"
msgid "Neva satimaṃ kalaṃ upenti na sahassimaṃ kalaṃ upenti na satasahassimaṃ kalaṃ upenti himavantaṃ pabbatarājānaṃ upanidhāya satta sāsapamattiyo pāsāṇasakkharā upanikkhittā”ti. "
msgstr "Compared to the Himalayas, it’s not nearly a hundredth, a thousandth, or a hundred thousandth part.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.9:2.4"
msgid "“Evameva kho … pe … "
msgstr "“In the same way, for a noble disciple, the suffering that’s over and done with is more …” "

msgctxt "sn13.9:2.5"
msgid "dhammacakkhupaṭilābho”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn13.9:2.6"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

